### C. Angular Module Import Reference

Import only modules used in the component's `imports: []` array. Never assume global registration.

```typescript
// Buttons
import { ButtonModule, CheckBoxModule, RadioButtonModule, SwitchModule,
         ChipListModule, FabModule, SpeedDialModule, SplitButtonModule,
         DropDownButtonModule } from '@syncfusion/ej2-angular-buttons';

