### F. Theme & Token Overrides

```scss
// ✅ Override Syncfusion tokens via CSS variables — always in styles.scss or a dedicated overrides file
:root {
  // Map your design token to Syncfusion's internal token
  --color-sf-primary: 103, 80, 164;          // RGB values — no # prefix
  --color-sf-primary-container: 234, 221, 255;
  --color-sf-on-primary: 255, 255, 255;
  --color-sf-surface: 255, 251, 254;
  --color-sf-on-surface: 28, 27, 31;
}

// Dark mode overrides
.e-dark-mode {
  --color-sf-primary: 208, 188, 255;
  --color-sf-surface: 28, 27, 31;
  --color-sf-on-surface: 230, 225, 229;
}

// ❌ Never override internal Syncfusion class names directly
.e-grid .e-headercell { background: purple; }  // breaks theme system

// ✅ Scope component overrides to :host ::ng-deep
:host ::ng-deep .e-grid .e-headercell {
  background: rgba(var(--color-sf-surface-variant), 1);
}
```

